          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Some cameras, including iPhone cameras, capture a gravity vector for",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "each image. This vector indicates the orientation of the camera at the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "moment you took the picture. RealityKit uses this gravity vector to",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "improve landmark matching with the other images in the session.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
